GNU Gettext provides facilities for translating program messages into a user's selected language. The home page is

: http://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/

Here are some things for working with Gettext in Emacs,

* PoMode -- edit <code>.po</code> catalogues
* [[po-mode+.el]] -- extra features for <nowiki>PoMode</nowiki>, by GauteHvoslefKvalnes
* MoMode -- view <code>.mo</code> compiled catalogues
